title: Samsung Galaxy S26: First render images found in One UI 8.5 beta
description: Rather bland render images of the Galaxy S26, Galaxy S26 Plus and Galaxy S26 Ultra have now appeared in a beta version of One UI 8.5. Additionally, Samsung is finally expected to catch up with Apple and Google by equipping the Galaxy S26 series with integrated magnets for full Qi2 compatibility.

title: Arne Slot reaction — 'A sense of unbelief' from Liverpool manager after latest dropped points
description: Arne Slot knows nothing's coming easy for Liverpool this season, and that's starting to feel proverbial after the Reds threw aside 2-0 and 3-2 leads in a 3-3 draw with Leeds at Elland Road on Saturday.

title: Letter: As a community, let’s put books in children’s hands
description: We can send them a book every month, straight to their home (from Niagara to Northwood), to spend their most formative years immersed in storytelling.

title: Soccer-Leipzig dismantle Frankfurt 6-0 with Diomande hat-trick
description: LEIPZIG, Germany, Dec 6 (Reuters) - RB Leipzig teenager Yan Diomande became the second youngest player in Bundesliga history to score a hat-trick when he netted three times in 18 minutes in their 6-0 demolition of visitors Eintracht Frankfurt 6-0 in the Bundesliga on Saturday as they tightened their hold on second spot in the Bundesliga. title: PM Modi expresses grief over Arpora fire tragedy in Goa
description: A devastating fire at a restaurant-cum-club in Arpora, Goa, claimed 23 lives, prompting Prime Minister Modi to express deep sorrow and offer support. The incident, believed to have started after a cylinder blast, has led to calls for safety audits of all clubs in the state.
